description: This app will allow Alexa to tell a few of the very funny jokes that millions or scientists are working on and perfecting behind this product. Unlike mathematics or physics, jokes are a pure science that not everyone gets.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask funny bone to tell jokes
Alexa, ask funny bone to tell me a joke
name: Funny Bone
shortDescription: Ever wanted Alexa to tell you a joke? Now she can tell you a very corny joke with this app. Be prepared.
